# CollabBoard Conventions

## Tech Stack

- React 19 + Vite + Bun + TypeScript
- Shadcn UI + Tailwind v4
- Konva.js for canvas rendering

## Styling

- Tailwind preferred. No inline styles or styled-jsx. Use Tailwind v4 syntax. Use Shadcn UI components when applicable.

## Konva.js

- Use `react-konva` for React integration. Keep Konva nodes in separate components. State in React, render to Konva.
- Use `listening={false}` for static objects; `perfectDrawEnabled={false}` for complex shapes when performance matters.

## File Structure

```text
src/
├── components/
│   ├── feature-name/   # Feature-specific components
│   └── ui/             # Shadcn and shared UI components
├── hooks/
├── lib/
├── types/
└── constants/
```

## Commit Messages

- `feat:` new features · `fix:` bug fixes · `perf:` performance · `refactor:` restructuring · `docs:` docs · `test:` tests. Branch off and merge into `development` only (see git-workflow).
